sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Organizer (User)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Event as Event Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    O ->> GW: POST /api/events (with CreateEventRequest JWT)
    GW ->> Auth: Validate JWT Token
    Auth -->> GW: Token Valid (User ID)
    GW ->> Event: Forward Request (with User ID)
    Event ->> Event: Validate request & capacity
    Event ->> DB: Save new Event (set organizerId)
    DB -->> Event: Saved Event Record
    Event -->> GW: 201 Created (Event Details)
    GW -->> O: Event Created Successfully